export default function RegisterPage() {
    return (
        <form>
            <label> Name
                <input type="text" name='name'/>
            </label>
            <label> Email
                <input type="email" name='email'/>
            </label>
            <label> Password
                <input type="password" name='password'/>
            </label>
            <button type="submit"></button>
        </form>
    )
}
